title: Star Wars - Shadow Stalker (1997) (Digital) (Minutemen-Syl3ntBob
description:
Promotional info - "Darth Vader has a covert agent to take care of his dirty work: Jix. Vader dispatches Jix to take care of an Imperial governor who has defected to the Rebel Alliance. But Jix finds a different, more important traitor, and winds up in a one-man war against a legion of stormtroopers. This one-shot collects the hit serial from Topps' Star Wars Galaxy magazine."

Ties into the Shadows of the Empire stories. Digital copy by Minutemen-Sly3ntBob. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
